Package com.gotenna.sdk.commands

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GTCommandCenter.GTDeleteLastMessageListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when an ACK is received from a GET MESSAGE command.
    GTCommandCenter.GTGroupInviteErrorListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a group invitation that was sent to a user triggers an error.
    GTCommandCenter.GTGroupInviteResponseListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a group invitation that was sent to a user receives a response.
    GTCommandCenter.GTMessageListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when an incoming message is received from the goTenna.
    GTCommandCenter.GTSystemInfoResponseListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a response is received after GTCommandCenter.sendGetSystemInfo(GTSystemInfoResponseListener, GTErrorListener) is called.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GTCommandCenter
    A singleton where all commands to the goTenna are sent from.
    GTError
    Represent a goTenna Error that should be handled.
